Package problem2

Interface BagOfWords

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConsBag, EmptyBag
    public interface BagOfWords
    Represents an immutable BagOfWords. A BagOfWords is a data container, holding Strings (words). A BagOfWords can contain duplicates, and Strings (words) have no order.
